<section class="c-section">
{{#if user}}
  <h2 class="c-section__title"><span>Hello, {{ user.username }}!</span></h2>
{{else}}
  <h2 class="c-section__title"><span>How it works!</span></h2>
{{/if}}
  <ul class="c-services">
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>Find Your Friends</h3>
      <p>You cant add songs to your friend's queue if you dont make your friendship offical! Go to Search Friends and add your friends!</p>
    </li>
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>Accept Friend Requests</h3>
      <p>Think you have a friend request? Go check out Friends and see if you have a pending request! If you have sent a friend request go to Friends and see if they accepted your friend request!</p>
    </li>
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>Add Songs to your Friend's Spotify Queue</h3>
      <p>Go to friends and select the friend you want. Then search for the song you want and click 'Add'. Its that simple!</p>
    </li>
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>Things you need to know!</h3>
      <p>For security purposes, your friend has to login to Queued Up atleast 1 hour before to accept song additons from friends!</p>
      <p>IMPORTANT: Your friend has to be currently playing music on Spotify to accept new songs.</p>
    </li>
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>Future Plans & Features</h3>
      <p>We want reach more customers! Features like automatic refresh token. Check back for more Updates!</p>
    </li>
    <li class="c-services__item">
      <h3>We want to hear from you!</h3>
      <p>Queued Up is determined to helping people out and making their lives eaiser! Let us know what we can do better!</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
